Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.28,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}但心中一直在呐喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:41.24,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}埋藏的感情释放悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:46.37,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}坚定的誓言紧握手心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.88,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.59,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.38,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}就能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.56,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}在那前方的未来
